# M-04 (05-MANUAL-OPS.md): Funded Base Sepolia EOA private key for FleetRegistry deploy.
# Generate or reuse a local EOA. Fund via Base Sepolia faucet (~0.01 ETH).
# Lives ONLY in contracts/.env (gitignored). Operator package has zero read access (OPER-05 boundary per D-13).
DEPLOYER_PRIVKEY=0x...

# Default https://sepolia.base.org; override to Alchemy/QuickNode for stability during recorded deploy (D-15).
BASE_SEPOLIA_RPC_URL=https://sepolia.base.org

# Optional — only needed for `forge verify-contract` against Basescan (used in Plan 02).
BASESCAN_API_KEY=
